  <entry>
    <title>BLOG开发记录</title>
    <link href="https://blog.whema.net/2023/07/13/2023/blog-todos/"/>
    <id>https://blog.whema.net/2023/07/13/2023/blog-todos/</id>
    <published>2023-07-13T08:24:41.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-08-03T15:50:55.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>记录搭建博客时遇到的问题，和下一步需要做的事情</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="Todos"><a href="#Todos" class="headerlink" title="Todos"></a>Todos</h2><ul><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> CDN加速</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 目录</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 在线编辑系统</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 评论区的设置按钮屏蔽</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> azure 自动部署</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> thumbnail: tag</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 代码块默认展开</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 代码块名字 - hexo 标签语法， icarus 参考？</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> logo</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 底部版权 -&gt; js 脚本？</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 文章加密插件</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 显示 <code>read more</code></li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 背景图片</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 网页加载加速？</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 评论系统</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 更改字体到 ‘霞鹜文楷’ ?</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 头像改成圆框</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> night 模式（整体切换？）</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 图片等链接改成英文 &#x2F; 加密</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 任务列表前面还有个点</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 主题问题</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 基本信息添加</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 网页图标</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 头像</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 异地同步测试</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 图床系统</li></ul><h2 id="Notes"><a href="#Notes" class="headerlink" title="Notes"></a>Notes</h2><ol><li><p>顶部导航栏固定</p><figure class="highlight styl"><figcaption><span>themes\icarus\source\css\imaegoo.styl</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.navbar</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">z-index</span>: <span class="number">100</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">position</span>: sticky</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">top</span>: <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.navbar-main</span></span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>没有显示<code>read more</code></p><figure class="highlight html"><figcaption><span>在文章适当位置插入</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--more--&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果还是没有：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><figcaption><span>_config.yml</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">read_more_btn:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>目录</p><p>需要在文章头部加入<code>toc: true</code>：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 一篇有目录的文章</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">toc: true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br><span class="line">文章内容...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>固定widgets：</p></li><li></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
